<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT27">
<l>māltāṉ pukunta maṭaneñcaṉ maṟṟatuvum</l>
<l>pēṟākak koḷvaṉō pētaikāḷ nīṟāṭi</l>
<l>tāṉkāṇa māṭṭāta tārakalac cēvaṭiyai</l>
<l>yāṉkāṇa vallēṟ kitu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O simpletons! Will I—who am able to see [His] garlanded, large red feet</l>
<l>which the ash-besmeared [Śiva] himself could not see—</l>
<l>esteem as a blessing [anything]</l>
<l>other than this, [namely,] my simple heart, which Māl Himself entered?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
